#!/usr/bin/env perl
use strict;
use warnings;
use OrePAN2::CLI::Indexer;

OrePAN2::CLI::Indexer->new->run(@ARGV);

__END__

=head1 NAME

orepan2-indexer - Indexer

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    % orepan2-indexer /path/to/darkpan/

=head1 DESCRIPTION

OrePAN2 indexer.

This module makes 02.package.txt from directory contains tar balls.

=head1 TUTORIAL

Create darkpan directory.

    % mkdir -p darkpan/authors/id/M/MA/MAHITO/

Download tar ball from CPAN.

    % curl -o darkpan/authors/id/M/MA/MAHITO/Acme-Hoge-0.03.tar.gz http://cpan.metacpan.org/authors/id/M/MA/MAHITO/Acme-Hoge-0.03.tar.gz

Create 02packages.details.txt!

    % orepan2-indexer darkpan/

Then you can install Acme::Hoge from darkpan!

    % cpanm --mirror-only --mirror=file://`pwd`/darkpan/ Acme::Hoge

